# Testing value smoothing

+ pulse metro
= 400 metro@rate

+ seq8 notes
= 3 notes@length
= 54 notes@step1
= 56 notes@step2
= 57 notes@step3
> metro@out notes@clock

+ seq8 times
= 4 times@length
= 60 times@step1
= 10 times@step2
= 120 times@step3
= 40 times@step4
> metro@out times@clock

+ miditofreq mtof
> notes@out mtof@in

+ sinosc osc
> mtof@out osc@freq
> metro@out osc@reset

+ segment env
= 1 env@val1
= 0 env@val2
= 200 env@dur
> metro@out env@clock

+ mult vca
> osc@out vca@in1
> env@out vca@in2

+ smooth sm
= 30 sm@dur
> times@out sm@in

+ fdelay dl
> sm@out dl@time
= 0.9 dl@feed
> vca@out dl@in

+ mix dw
= 0.5 dw@coeff
> vca@out dw@in1
> dl@out dw@in2

> dw@out _out_@l
> dw@out _out_@r
